data.description: Welcome to your almost new dream home nestled conveniently close to the Peterson and Schriever, offering unparalleled views of majestic Pikes Peak. This immaculate two-story residence boasts modern elegance and comfort, perfect for those seeking both luxury and convenience.    As you step inside, you're greeted by a spacious, airy floor plan designed for seamless living and entertaining. The main level features an inviting living area and large office with breathtaking panorama of Pikes Peak, creating a picturesque backdrop for everyday moments and special occasions.    The gourmet kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's delight, equipped with stainless steel appliances, sleek granite countertops, and ample cabinet space for all your storage needs. Adjacent to the kitchen, the dining area provides a cozy ambiance for enjoying meals with loved ones while soaking in the stunning mountain vistas.    Venture upstairs to discover a serene retreat in the form of three generously sized bedrooms, each offering plush carpeting, ample closet space, and large windows that flood the rooms with natural light. The master suite is a tranquil haven, featuring a luxurious ensuite bathroom complete with a luxury shower, and dual vanity. Also, enjoy the upstairs loft! Perfect for additional live/work space.     For added versatility and recreation, the fully finished basement provides two additional bedrooms and living space ideal for a home theater, game room, or gym, offering endless possibilities to suit your lifestyle.    Outside, the meticulously landscaped yard beckons you to enjoy Colorado's outdoor lifestyle, whether hosting barbecues on the patio or simply relaxing in the sunshine while admiring the awe-inspiring mountain views.    With its prime location near the Bases, convenient access to amenities, and unrivaled vistas of Pikes Peak, this almost new home offers a rare opportunity to experience the epitome of modern mountain living.
